<doc f='vlc/modules/access/linsys/linsys_sdiaudio.h' l='48'>/* The minimum transmit buffer size must be positive, divisible by 4,
 * and large enough that the buffers aren&apos;t transferred to the onboard FIFOs
 * too quickly for the machine to handle the interrupts.
 * This is especially a problem at startup, when the FIFOs are empty.
 * Relevant factors include onboard FIFO size, PCI bus throughput,
 * processor speed, and interrupt latency. */</doc>
